'''Christianity'''

# An enormous cult started in the year 0 A.D.  While giving the people a good source of morale values, it also drills false beliefs into their brains, and brainwashes them into believing in an afterlife.  Jesus Christ started this cult, and is believed to be the son of, and the god himself.
